title: Commanded To Be Blessed | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Commanded To Be Blessed | Joel Osteen
description:
Nothing can stop God’s commanded blessing over your life. All it takes is one touch of His favor to get you exactly where you're supposed to be.


Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.
